itle\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"score\": 0.9996660470955422, \"rank\": 0.00032846679965998447, \"text\": \"British\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Boxing_Board_of_Control\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some time\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3687}, {\"ngram\": \"his family\", \"from\": 3705, \"to\": 3715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Ultimately, the decision had to come from me,' Murray toldCNNlast week about his retirement from professional tennis.\", \"from\": 3718, \"to\": 3836, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3766, \"end\": 3772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.875625727295227e-51, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 3731, \"to\": 3743}, {\"ngram\": \"his retirement\", \"from\": 3796, \"to\": 3810}, {\"ngram\": \"professional tennis\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3835}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'I am happy that I get to finish playing an Olympics with a lot of my\\u2026 I consider a lot of the tennis players on our team close friends of mine.\", \"from\": 3837, \"to\": 3981, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an Olympics\", \"from\": 3878, \"to\": 3889}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3895, \"to\": 3900}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3919, \"to\": 3924}, {\"ngram\": \"the tennis players\", \"from\": 3928, \"to\": 3946}, {\"ngram\": \"our team\", \"from\": 3950, \"to\": 3958}, {\"ngram\": \"close friends\", \"from\": 3959, \"to\": 3972}, {\"ngram\": \"mine\", \"from\": 3976, \"to\": 3980}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Getting to be around them [makes me happy] and I have great memories from the Olympics.\", \"from\": 3983, \"to\": 4071, 